{"tid":1245773,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"統計了C朗和美斯國家隊所有比賽詳細數據包括時間進球以及對手當時排名","createTime":"2019-06-20T12:33:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-24T05:51:57.000Z","uid":173952,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"f49daf2a3e5fc9e13321f7dc9ad559710b9e47fa","tid":1245773,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T12:33:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/List_of_international_goals_scored_by_Cristiano_Ronaldo#cite_note-46\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FList_of_international_goals_scored_by_Cristiano_Ronaldo%23cite_note-46&d=cvYurzZEI7gK%2Fp8SijS8D8RCHeky4xD%2FQbA%2BfbsvJuc%3D&h=f62a86d5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/List_of_international_goals_scored_by_Cristiano_Ronaldo#cite_note-46</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/List_of_international_goals_scored_by_Lionel_Messi\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FList_of_international_goals_scored_by_Lionel_Messi&d=cvYurzZEI7gK%2Fp8SijS8D8RCHeky4xD%2FQbA%2BfbsvJuc%3D&h=9d4a9ea3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/List_of_international_goals_scored_by_Lionel_Messi</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.fifa.com/fifa-world-ranking/ranking-table/men/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fifa.com%2Ffifa-world-ranking%2Franking-table%2Fmen%2F&d=cvYurzZEI7gK%2Fp8SijS8D8RCHeky4xD%2FQbA%2BfbsvJuc%3D&h=ccf53cea\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.fifa.com/fifa-world-ranking/ranking-table/men/</a><br />\n<br />\n由於缺少2007年6月之前的月度排名，以國際足聯給出的年度排名代替。<br />\n對陣球隊當時排名採用比賽之前最近的國際足聯排名。<br />\n希望雙方球迷理性看待數據！<br />\n先上統計結論：<br />\nC朗對陣前10進球10粒，美斯對陣前10進球5粒。<br />\nC朗對陣前50進球35粒，美斯對陣前50進球26粒。<br />\n需要指出的是之前爭議較大的美斯對陣厄瓜多爾世預賽的帽子戲法發生在2017年10月10號，在前一個國際足聯排名日（2017-09-14）排名35名，在此之後一個國際足聯排名日（2017-10-16）排名60名，根據我們的數據選取規則，選擇了35名作為當時排名。"},{"pid":"395d225f70d118823e89e8f6e416211222ccc23a","tid":1245773,"uid":173952,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T12:36:21.000Z","msg":"我轉貼的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wdm4Xz1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fwdm4Xz1.png&h=c1ac9ce7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pFmP8GG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpFmP8GG.png&h=f3e896c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Yq42Ke2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYq42Ke2.png&h=1673be00&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UDsDhz3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUDsDhz3.png&h=6f058233&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0971cd2d06da19b9cd1df42fab8b7fb6402e51e9","tid":1245773,"uid":34571,"like":0,"dislike":11,"score":-11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T12:37:11.000Z","msg":"樓主既然唔死可否不再分化朗美迷"},{"pid":"30e71707fc88a6f70bdcbb2436259c081b18e501","tid":1245773,"uid":173952,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"0971cd2d06da19b9cd1df42fab8b7fb6402e51e9","tid":1245773,"uid":34571,"like":0,"dislike":11,"score":-11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T12:37:11.000Z","msg":"樓主既然唔死可否不再分化朗美迷"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T12:38:21.000Z","msg":"希望雙方球迷理性看待數據！"},{"pid":"fc8ad3006f9550df9fe68271b7d3000cfc2891e0","tid":1245773,"uid":166126,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T12:41:44.000Z","msg":"唔過兩頁"},{"pid":"5ee28cf092425af0759dc28e99f4c8b283a898fd","tid":1245773,"uid":43785,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"0971cd2d06da19b9cd1df42fab8b7fb6402e51e9","tid":1245773,"uid":34571,"like":0,"dislike":11,"score":-11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T12:37:11.000Z","msg":"樓主既然唔死可否不再分化朗美迷"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T12:48:03.000Z","msg":"我覺得要分過高下，<br />\nC朗地位不能與美斯相比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/